subproject.description:
Development cooperation activities of the Czech Trust Fund according to the cost-sharing agreement ToR programmed, facilitated and implemented. The activities are focused on following priority areas: environment protection, good/local government, democracy governance, HIV prevention.
The main objective is to transfer the best Czech experiences.
subproject.title: Czech Contribution to EDI
